thread.title: 'Walking Dead' Season 6 premiere held in NYC
thread.title_full: 'Walking Dead' Season 6 premiere held in NYC - UPI.com

author: Karen Butler
title: 'Walking Dead' Season 6 premiere held in NYC
text:
1 of 10 | License Photo NEW YORK, Oct. 10 (UPI) -- The Walking Dead cast members Norman Reedus, Andrew Lincoln and Danai Gurira attended the show's Season 6 fan premiere in New York City Friday.
Also photographed on the red carpet were series regulars Melissa McBride, Chandler Riggs and Steven Yeun.
Tens of thousands of devotees of the show packed Madison Square Garden to watch the first installment of the latest season of the zombie-apocalypse drama.
Season 6 will kick off on AMC Sunday night.
